==Description==
To use this template, copy the following code and fill in the appropriate fields.

==Syntax==
<pre>
{{infobox character
 | title         = 
 | image         = [e.g. "Example.jpg"]
 | imagewidth    = [e.g. "150"] [default: 210 pixels]
 | imagecaption  = 
 | position      =
 | age           =
 | status        =
 | height        =
 | weight        =
}}
</pre>

==Samples==
<pre>
{{infobox character
 | title         = Flowa
 | image         = Example.jpg
 | imagecaption  = Flowa, at rest
 | position      = Legal Secretary
 | age           = 2 months
 | status        = Active
 | height        = 5 inches
 | weight        = 20 grams
}}
</pre>

